    public abstract class AbstractPopup
extends javax.swing.AbstractAction
    AbstractPopup is the superclass of the actions performed by PopupMenu on the Canvas. This class is abstract because it does not define the ActionPerformed(ActionEvent evt) method. In every subClass of AbstractPopup this method performs a specific action. Subclasses of AbstractPopup are:
